parser

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.Constants

  • public class Constants
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the constant regular expressions that the parser will use. Regular expression allows for flexibility for the use when entering expressions and reduce the amount of if-else in the command parser.
    Author:
    sylvesterchin
